YO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Borton sedang memberikan sambutan di acara 35 tahun Dragon Group (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2066\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-4.jpg\" alt=\"Borton sedang memberikan sambutan di acara 35 tahun Dragon Group (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2066\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Borton sedang memberikan sambutan di acara 35 tahun Dragon Group (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_331\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-331\" data-attachment-id=\"331\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/tahun-2017-waktunya-berkolaborasi-dengan-ciayo-comics/attachment/collab4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Collab4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kolaborasi Edwin (kedua dari kanan) Jhody (kanan) dengan CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kolaborasi Edwin (kedua dari kanan) Jhody (kanan) dengan CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Collab4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Collab4.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-331 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Collab4.jpg\" alt=\"Borton dan Victor (Co-Founder) sedang berbincang-bincang dengan Bang Edwin dan Bang Jhody untuk berkolaborasi yang akhirnya menghasilkan komik Edwin Jhody (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Collab4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Collab4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-331\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Borton dan Victor (Co-Founder) sedang berbincang-bincang dengan Bang Edwin dan Bang Jhody untuk berkolaborasi yang akhirnya menghasilkan komik Edwin Jhody (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tahun 2017 adalah tahun yang sangat tepat untuk melakukan kolaborasi dengan kami. CIAYO Comics bukan hanya memiliki platform komik digital Indonesia  namun kami juga memiliki layanan pengelolaan Intellectual Property (IP) komik yang terpadu dengan CIAYO Games dan CIAYO Blog.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1424\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1424\" data-attachment-id=\"1424\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sidak-faza-meonk-inspeksi-mendadak-ke-kantor-ciayo-comics/attachment/faza8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Faza8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Faza8\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Faza8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Faza8.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-1424 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Faza8.jpg\" alt=\"Borton dan Faza Meonk berpose bersama tim CIAYO Comics dan Pionicon yang akhirnya menghasilkan kolaborasi komik Si Juki &amp; Mang Awung (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Faza8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Faza8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1424\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Borton dan Faza Meonk berpose bersama tim CIAYO Comics dan Pionicon yang akhirnya menghasilkan kolaborasi komik Si Juki &amp; Mang Awung (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Saat ini CIAYO Comics sedang bekerjasama dengan beberapa penerbit dan pemilik IP lokal untuk mengembangkan IP-IP tersebut di platform komik digital kami. Harapannya agar komik-komik dengan karakter lokal ini bisa bersuara lantang di panggung mancanegara.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_2064\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2064\" data-attachment-id=\"2064\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/undangan-terbuka-untuk-komikus-dan-penerbit-komik-di-seluruh-indonesia/attachment/body1-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&q